category: Graphics Libs
requires: libjpeg8 liblcms2_2 libtiff6 cygwin
sdesc: "Little color management engine (utilities)"
ldesc: "Little CMS intends to be a small-footprint color management engine, with special
focus on accuracy and performance. It uses the International Color Consortium
standard (ICC), which is the modern standard when regarding to color management.
The ICC specification is widely used and is referred to in many International and
other de-facto standards."
